msgid "Generating Jakarta REST resources with Panache"
msgstr "Gerando recursos Jakarta REST com Panache"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/rest-data-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A lot of web applications are monotonous CRUD applications with REST APIs that are tedious to write.\n"
"To streamline this task, REST Data with Panache extension can generate the basic CRUD endpoints for your entities and repositories."
msgstr ""
"Muitas aplicações web são aplicações CRUD monótonas com APIs REST entediantes de escrever.\n"
"Para agilizar essa tarefa, a extensão REST Data with Panache pode gerar os endpoints CRUD básicos para suas entidades e repositórios."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/rest-data-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Currently, this extension supports Hibernate ORM and MongoDB with Panache and can generate CRUD resources that work with `application/json` and `application/hal+json` content and generates REST Resources backed by Quarkus REST."
msgstr "Atualmente, esta extensão suporta Hibernate ORM e MongoDB com Panache e pode gerar recursos CRUD que funcionam com conteúdos `application/json` e `application/hal+json`, e gera recursos REST baseados no Quarkus REST."

